Package: ruby-ethon
Version: 0.18.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: ruby, libcurl, libffi, sed, findutils
Section: ruby
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/typhoeus/ethon
Description: Ruby HTTP client library (libcurl wrapper)
 Ethon is a lightweight HTTP client wrapper around libcurl,
 providing easy access to curl features. It is used by the
 Typhoeus HTTP client.
